sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects requests to exclude files, folders or processes from Antivirus scanning using PowerShell cmdlets

match_context.values: @{CommandLine=powershell -Command Add-MpPreference -ExclusionProcess 'powershell.exe'; Add-MpPreference -ExclusionProcess 'cmd.exe'; Add-MpPreference -ExclusionProcess 'svchost.exe'; Add-MpPreference -ExclusionProcess 'services.exe'; Add-MpPreference -ExclusionPath 'C:\Windows\System32'; Add-MpPreference -ExclusionPath 'C:\Users\<USER>\AppData\Roaming\Microsoft\Windows\Explorer'; Image=powershell; EventID=1}
